00:00:18.460 --> 00:00:21.680
So well over 80% of all T-follicular helper

00:00:21.680 --> 00:00:25.500
and peripheral T-cell lymphoma, NOS, do express CD5.

00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:28.840
And if it is expressed, it's usually very strongly expressed.

00:00:28.840 --> 00:00:33.840
